---
// Philosophy — manifesto section with generous whitespace
---

<section id="philosophy" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="manifesto">

      <div class="manifesto__header reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Philosophy</p>
        <h2 class="manifesto__title gradient-text">Wellness as a Daily Ritual</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="manifesto__statement reveal">
        <p>
          We believe healing is not an event — it is a practice.
          A quiet morning, a steady breath, a return to the body.
          At Solace, every offering is designed to remind you of the wisdom you already carry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="manifesto__pillars stagger">
        <div class="manifesto__pillar reveal">
          <div class="manifesto__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="19" stroke="#9DB4A0" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M20 8 C20 8 11 14 11 21 a9 9 0 0 0 18 0 c0-7-9-13-9-13z" fill="#9DB4A0" opacity="0.3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Body</h4>
          <p>Somatic awareness and gentle movement to release what the body holds.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__pillar reveal">
          <div class="manifesto__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="19" stroke="#9DB4A0" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M13 23 Q15 16 20 16 Q25 16 27 23" stroke="#9DB4A0" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="27" r="2.2" fill="#9DB4A0"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Breath</h4>
          <p>Pranayama and conscious breathing to regulate the nervous system with ease.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__pillar reveal">
          <div class="manifesto__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="19" stroke="#9DB4A0" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="9" stroke="#9DB4A0" stroke-width="1.2" fill="rgba(157,180,160,0.07)"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="3.5" fill="#9DB4A0" opacity="0.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Mind</h4>
          <p>Mindfulness and nervous-system regulation to cultivate lasting inner calm.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="manifesto__quote reveal">
        <p>"The wound is the place where the light enters you."</p>
        <cite>— Rumi</cite>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    gap: var(--space-16);
  }

  .manifesto__header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .manifesto__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .manifesto__statement {
    max-width: 58ch;
  }

  .manifesto__statement p {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .manifesto__pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-10);
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  .manifesto__pillar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .manifesto__icon {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .manifesto__pillar h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .manifesto__pillar p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .manifesto__quote {
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(157, 180, 160, 0.25);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(157, 180, 160, 0.25);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .manifesto__quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .manifesto__quote cite {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-sage);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .manifesto__pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); }
  }
</style>
